data.text:
Star Wars: Episode IV - A New Hope

All items are signed by the guests direct for us and come with one of our small holographic proof labels attached to the reverse of the item signed. Guaranteed to pass ACOA Authentication . But rest assured you are buying direct from the source.

Please note we have several of each item and placement of autograph may change slightly.

Please feel free to contact us with any questions you may have.
